      "descriptionFilterHtml": "展覽名稱 ▻ 臺灣建築模型典藏展\r\n\r\n                  The Archives of Taiwan Classical Architecture Models Exhibition\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n常設展\r\n\r\n展覽地點 ▻渭水樓 S03\r\n\r\n主辦單位 ▻文化部文化資產局\r\n\r\n策展單位 ▻展開設計有限公司\r\n\r\n協力單位 ▻即木工藝、澄品廣告、映築設計\r\n\r\n聯絡電話 ▻04-2217-6967\r\n\r\n\r\n展覽內容 ▻\r\n\r\n本次展覽由文化部文化資產局主辦，展覽空間策劃由展開設計有限公司策展，邀集文化設計各領域協力單位協同策劃，包括即木工藝、澄品廣告、映築設計。展場空間透過立體透空展架的視覺框景，重新呈現王大閎、陳其寬、貝聿銘等當代建築大師的模型巨作，並與日治時期臺灣經典建築，展開跨時空的世紀對話。並希冀藉由本次建築典藏展，開啟大眾對建築的時代記憶與歷史認知。\r\n\r\nOrganized by Bureau of Cultural Heritage, Ministry of Culture, this exhibition is curated by Denkwii Architecture and Design; and jointly curated by That Wood, CHENG PIN Advertising Design and Reflec Design. Through the enframed scenery created by 3D open-worked exhibition stands, the exhibition space not only presents masterpiece models of Wang Da-Hong, Chen Chi-Kwan and Pei Ieoh Ming in a different way, but also depicts the century dialogue with classic architectural buildings built in Taiwan during the Japanese domination period across time and space. It is expected that this Classical Architecture Models Exhibition will demonstrate the uniqueness of classical architecture across time and enhance the audience’s historical awareness.",
